OL,3,CHosepipe ban lifted by the UK's
OL,4,Cbiggest water provider
OL,6,FThames Water has lifted its hosepipe
OL,7,Fban following 'above-average rainfall
OL,8,Fand strong customer support in
OL,9,Fconserving water. '
OL,11,FThe restriction for customers with OX,
OL,12,FGL, SN, RG4, RG8 and RG9 postcodes has
OL,13,Fbeen in force since 22 July 2025, due
OL,14,Fto prolonged dry weather across the
OL,15,Fregion in the spring and summer months.
