OL,3,CHosepipe ban lifted by the UK's
OL,4,Cbiggest water provider
OL,6,FRecent rainfall has helped restore
OL,7,Fgroundwater levels, with the utility
OL,8,Fcompany saying its Farmoor Reservoir,
OL,9,Fin Oxfordshire, has reached 90%
OL,10,Fstorage, which is average for the time
OL,11,Fof year.
OL,13,FThe UK's largest water company has
OL,14,Fthanked customers for their water-
OL,15,Fsaving efforts during the ban, but is
OL,16,Fencouraging them to continue to use
OL,17,Fwater wisely to protect resources
OL,18,Fahead of summer 2026.
