OL,3,CHosepipe ban lifted by the UK's
OL,4,Cbiggest water provider
OL,6,FThames Water says it's taken on
OL,7,F'extensive' measures to boost its
OL,8,Fwater resources, including reducing
OL,9,Fleaks across the network. It says
OL,10,Fleaks are down 13.2% since 2020, its
OL,11,Flowest ever level.
OL,13,FIt also says its rolling out a smart
OL,14,Fmeter programme across the Thames
OL,15,FValley, where customers can track
OL,16,Ftheir water use in real time, helping
OL,17,Fthem to spot leaks in their own pipes
OL,18,Fand save money.
