OL,3,CHosepipe ban lifted by the UK's
OL,4,Cbiggest water provider
OL,6,FNevil Muncaster, who's the Strategic
OL,7,FWater Resources Director at Thames
OL,8,FWater, said: "We would like to say a
OL,9,Fbig thank you to our customers for
OL,10,Ftheir support in helping to protect
OL,11,Fwater supplies over the past few
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,F"The rain over the last few weeks has
OL,15,Fhelped restore groundwater levels in
OL,16,Fthe region, which were still
OL,17,Frecovering after a record-breaking
OL,18,Fsummer, and allows us to now lift
OL,19,Fusage restrictions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
