OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F414A1764246550
OL,3,CHosepipe ban lifted by the UK's
OL,4,Cbiggest water provider
OL,6,F"While groundwater levels feeding the
OL,7,FRiver Thames, which is the source of
OL,8,Fwater for Farmoor reservoir, have
OL,9,Frecovered we will continue to monitor
OL,10,Frainfall and groundwater levels over
OL,11,Fthe coming months to make sure we are
OL,12,Fstill in a good position for 2026.
OL,14,F"We're encouraging all our customers
OL,15,Fto keep using water wisely over the
OL,16,Fwinter months so water resources in
OL,17,Four region continue to recharge ready
OL,18,Ffor spring and summer next year."
